<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>QR Code Generator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/utils.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/d5a98b8c2b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="w-full px-32 flex items-center py-6 bg-secondary h-auto mb-4 lg:h-32">
      <img class="h-16
      " src="/logo.png">
    </header>
    <main class="container py-6 min-w-container px-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <header class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="uppercase text-center font-bold text-4xl text-main">QR Code Generator</h1>
        <span class="block font-normal text-2xl text-secondary">Simple and easy to use!</span>
      </header>

      <section class="flex flex-col px-24 min-w-container">
        <p class="pt-6 text-gray-400">Please type the URL or Text below and click Generate!</p>
        <form class="form" action="/scan" method="POST">
          <input name="url" class="form-control shadow-md rounded-md px-2 w-full h-12 mt-2 text-gray-700 hover:shadow-lg duration-500" placeholder="URL or Text" type="text" required>
          <br>
          <button type="submit" class="bg-secondary h-14 text-white font-semibold px-6 shadow-md rounded-2xl w-48 mt-6 first-letter hover:text-rose-200" value="Get QR">Generate</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col px-24 py-3">
        <ul class="list-none py-6">
          <li>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-semibold text-secondary text-2xl">Why us?</h2>
              <p class="py-2 leading-loose text-gray-700">Our QR code application is easy to use and lets you create custom QR codes in just a few clicks. It offers a range of customization options so you can personalize your codes. Perfect for hobby projects.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="list-none py-8">
              <h2 class="font-semibold text-secondary text-2xl">Contribute to us!</h2>
              <p class="py-2 leading-loose text-gray-700">We would love to hear from you! Please share your feedback and ideas on how we can make our QR code application even better. Your contributions will help us continue to improve and enhance our application.</p>
              <a href="https://paypal.me/FranL028"><button type="submit" class="bg-secondary h-14 text-white font-semibold px-6 shadow-md rounded-2xl w-48 mt-4 hover:text-rose-200">Our paypal</button></a>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-main min-h-full flex flex-col py-32">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white m-auto">Support us:</span>
      <div class="flex items-center m-auto">
        <ul class="flex justify-center gap-12 pt-4">
          <li><a href="https://twitter.com"><i class="fab fa-twitter text-white text-2xl hover:scale-110 duration-200"></i></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in text-white text-2xl hover:scale-110 duration-200"></i></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.github.com"><i class="fab fa-github text-white text-2xl hover:scale-110 duration-200"></i></a></li>
          </ul>
